Description:
Our Precious earth!
Soon to be destroyed by thousands of meteorites.
There is nothing you can do to make it stop!
We are all going to die!

Do you want to spend the time you have left with the ones you love? 
Or do you go down swinging by avoiding as many of these meteorite *****s! 

Features:
*Cartoon action all over the screen 
*Background destruction 
*20 Playable characters 
*16 Bonus pick-ups! 
*Saved statistics 
*Collect coins to unlock goodies 
*Easy help file to get you going 
*Awesome music by David.F.Burrows 
*Highscore function
